               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18200217-72-person810">
                  HENRY 
                  ANDREWS
               <interp inst="t18200217-72-person810" type="surname" value="ANDREWS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200217-72-person810" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200217-72-person810" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a lamplighter. On the 8th of February, in the afternoon, I saw the prisoners looking in at Sherwin's window - Wilson crossed, and came out of the shop with the bacon. A third man joined them. I secured Wilcox, and Christie secured Wilson - the other escaped with the bacon. I am sure they were together.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18200217-72-person811">
                  JACOB 
                  SHERWIN
               <interp inst="t18200217-72-person811" type="surname" value="SHERWIN"></interp>
