                     <interp inst="t18200217-72-person811" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I lost the bacon out of my shop.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18200217-72-person812">
                  ROBERT 
                  CHRISTIE
               <interp inst="t18200217-72-person812" type="surname" value="CHRISTIE"></interp>
